name: Own Balance
description:
we always maintain a balance in a relationship, be it friends, girlfriends, family, and the environment, they always pay attention to what we do consciously or not.

until finally we are faced with a choice between ourselves and others.

many also want to attract us in circumstances we do not want. making a good things is difficult, when the environment is not supportive, the best way is to balance everything, and be yourself
